snippet.title: Best VGM 893 - Dragon Quest II - Chateau
snippet.description:
Symphonic Suite version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=60FoWZsxoiA

See also:
Best VGM 256 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-VtNcqxyNnA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Dragon Quest II (1993)
Chateau
Koichi Sugiyama
